"title": "9315: resurrection, of believers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9315: resurrection, of believers",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The future event of finally being raised to glory with Jesus Christ. Believers may rest assured that, on account of their faith, they will share in the resurrection and glory of Christ and be with him for ever.</p>\n<h2>The nature of the resurrection of believers</h2>\n<h3>A resurrection to eternal life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25-John11:26\">JHN 11:25–11:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:3\">DAN 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:35-Luke20:36\">LUK 20:35–20:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24-John5:25\">JHN 5:24–5:25</a></p>\n<h3>Being completely united to Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:5\">ROM 6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:39\">JHN 6:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:44\">JHN 6:44</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:23\">ACT 26:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:8\">ROM 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:14\">1CO 6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:20-1Cor15:23\">1CO 15:20–15:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:14\">2CO 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:4\">COL 3:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:16\">1TH 4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:11\">2TI 2:11</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to becoming like Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:49</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps17:15\">PSA 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:24-Matt22:30\">MAT 22:24–22:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:18-Mark12:25\">MRK 12:18–12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:51-1Cor15:53\">1CO 15:51–15:53</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:21\">PHP 3:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:2\">1JN 3:2</a></p>\n<h2>The resurrection as the future hope of believers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:19\">1CO 15:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:13-1Thess4:14\">1TH 4:13–4:14</a></strong> <em>In the NT the death of believers is often likened to sleep.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:23-Job19:27\">JOB 19:23–19:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:15\">PSA 49:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:20\">PSA 71:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa26:19\">ISA 26:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:3\">DAN 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:14\">HOS 13:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:24\">JHN 11:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:6\">ACT 23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:15\">ACT 24:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:1-2Cor5:4\">2CO 5:1–5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:10\">2TI 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>The resurrection as an incentive to godliness and perseverance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:58\">1CO 15:58</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:12-Luke14:14\">LUK 14:12–14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:30-1Cor15:32\">1CO 15:30–15:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:6-2Cor5:10\">2CO 5:6–5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:20-Phil1:21\">PHP 1:20–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:35\">HEB 11:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:3\">1JN 3:3</a></p>\n<h2>The resurrection as an incentive to endurance of suffering</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17\">ROM 8:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:11-2Tim2:12\">2TI 2:11–2:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:24-John12:25\">JHN 12:24–12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:22\">ACT 14:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:12-1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:12–4:13</a></p>",
